OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fsome brightness. Clouding over from
OL,7,Fthe southwest this afternoon but it
OL,8,Fwill remain dry. Fresh south or
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,12,Fwith the odd shower. Staying cloudy
OL,13,Fovernight with some occasional rain
OL,14,Flater in the night. Fresh occasionally
OL,15,Fstrong southerly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA cloudy day with occasional
OL,18,Frain, but some drier spells of weather
OL,19,Ftoo. Strong southwesterly winds at
OL,20,Ffirst.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
