OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny spells on Friday
OL,7,Fand Saturday. Cloudy and mainly dry on
OL,8,FSunday with the odd shower. Strong
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly winds across Shetland on
OL,10,FSaturday.
